HE'S GOT SPECIAL ISSUES.

206
00:11:26,374 --> 00:11:29,807
YOU'RE BETTER OFF
IF YOU DON'T GET INVOLVED
WITH HIM.

207
00:11:29,841 --> 00:11:33,207
[ HUFFS ]
SPECIAL ISSUES, MY ASS.

208
00:11:33,241 --> 00:11:37,574
THE THING IS, BON WANTS TO BE
AN EXORCIST BECAUSE HE SAYS
HE WANTS TO DEFEAT SATAN.

209
00:11:37,607 --> 00:11:39,241
[ GASPS ]

210
00:11:39,274 --> 00:11:41,907
I'M GONNA BEAT THE SHIT
OUT OF SATAN!

211
00:11:41,941 --> 00:11:45,041
CRAP, HE'S... JUST LIKE ME.

212
00:11:45,074 --> 00:11:47,707
[ CHUCKLES ]
YEAH, IT'S KINDA FUNNY,
ISN'T IT?

213
00:11:47,741 --> 00:11:49,274
UH, WHAT'S SO FUNNY
ABOUT IT?

214
00:11:49,307 --> 00:11:51,541
[ LAUGHS ]
HUH?
IT ISN'T FUNNY.

215
00:11:51,574 --> 00:11:54,341
THE WHOLE THING ABOUT BON
AND WHY HE'S SO INTENSE...

216
00:11:54,374 --> 00:11:56,241
IS THAT HE WANTS TO RESTORE
OUR TEMPLE.

217
00:11:56,274 --> 00:11:58,541
IT WAS ALL BUT RUINED
AFTER THE BLUE NIGHT.

218
00:11:58,574 --> 00:12:00,807
BLUE NIGHT?
WHAT'S THAT?

219
00:12:00,841 --> 00:12:02,474
HUH?
YOU DON'T KNOW?

220
00:12:02,507 --> 00:12:04,674
YOU'RE LIKE THE ONLY ONE
WHO DOESN'T.

221
00:12:04,707 --> 00:12:08,474
HERE'S WHAT HAPPENED.
SIXTEEN YEARS AGO SATAN CROSSED
THE BARRIER TO OUR WORLD...

222
00:12:08,507 --> 00:12:10,574
AND MASSACRED
ALL THE TOP CLERGYMEN.

223
00:12:10,607 --> 00:12:12,207
WE'VE CALLED IT
THE BLUE NIGHT EVER SINCE.

224
00:12:12,241 --> 00:12:14,374
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, "MASSACRED"?

225
00:12:14,407 --> 00:12:16,941
WE HEARD ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED
FROM BON'S FATHER.

226
00:12:16,974 --> 00:12:19,007
HE WAS THE HEAD MONK
OF OUR TEMPLE.

227
00:12:19,041 --> 00:12:23,774
SIXTEEN YEARS AGO,
THE MOST POWERFUL EXORCISTS
STARTED BLEEDING ALL OVER.

228
00:12:23,807 --> 00:12:28,274
BLUE FLAMES SHOT
FROM THEIR HEADS,
AND THEN THEY ALL DIED.

229
00:12:28,307 --> 00:12:31,241
THE BLUE FLAMES
ARE A SURE SIGN
THAT SATAN'S AROUND.

230
00:12:31,274 --> 00:12:34,174
OUR MONK, WHO WAS YOUNG
AND STILL IN TRAINING,

231
00:12:34,207 --> 00:12:36,141
WASN'T STRONG ENOUGH
TO FIGHT BACK.

232
00:12:36,174 --> 00:12:38,974
HE JUST HID IN A CORNER
TILL DAWN, PRAYING.

233
00:12:39,007 --> 00:12:43,441
AFTER THAT NIGHT,
HE FINISHED HIS TRAINING
AND TOOK OVER THE TEMPLE.

234
00:12:43,474 --> 00:12:46,307
BUT FOLKS WERE STILL
FREAKED OUT BY WHAT HAPPENED.

235
00:12:46,341 --> 00:12:49,007
SO PARISHIONERS STOPPED COMING,
AND, AS WORD GOT AROUND,

236
00:12:49,041 --> 00:12:51,541
EVEN VISITORS
STOPPED SHOWING UP.

237
00:12:51,574 --> 00:12:55,974
AND THE NEXT THING YOU KNOW,
PEOPLE WERE CALLING IT
THE CURSED TEMPLE.

238
00:12:56,007 --> 00:12:58,941
SHIMA AND I ARE APPRENTICE MONKS
AT BON'S TEMPLE.

239
00:12:58,974 --> 00:13:02,241
WE FOLLOWED HIM TO THE ACADEMY
THINKING WE COULD
BECOME EXORCISTS...

240
00:13:02,274 --> 00:13:04,741
AND HELP HIM TO RESTORE IT
TO ITS FORMER GLORY.

241
00:13:04,774 --> 00:13:07,974
BON'S GOT A FULL PLATE.
THAT'S WHY HE'S SO INTENSE.

242
00:13:08,007 --> 00:13:10,174
BUT HE'S A GOOD GUY
ONCE YOU GET TO KNOW HIM.

243
00:13:10,207 --> 00:13:12,407
THE BOY FROM THE CURSED TEMPLE,
HUH?

244
00:13:25,625 --> 00:13:27,225
[ LOUD THUDS ]

245
00:13:29,125 --> 00:13:30,591
[ PANTING ]

246
00:13:30,625 --> 00:13:32,225
[ SCREAMS ]

247
00:13:40,139 --> 00:13:42,939
EXCUSE ME, HOW MANY TIMES
ARE YOU GOING TO TRIP?

248
00:13:42,972 --> 00:13:45,339
- I'M SORRY, SIR.
- IS THERE A REASON...

249
00:13:45,372 --> 00:13:47,572
WHY YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE IN CLASS
NOT WEARING SWEATS?

250
00:13:47,606 --> 00:13:51,206
I, UH, I DON'T REALLY HAVE
ANYTHING ELSE
I CAN WEAR FOR SPORTS.

251
00:13:51,239 --> 00:13:54,772
THAT OUTFIT WAS FASHIONABLE
A HUNDRED YEARS AGO.

252
00:13:54,806 --> 00:13:56,639
SHIMA AND YAMADA,
YOU'RE UP NEXT.

253
00:13:56,672 --> 00:13:58,272
OKAY.

254
00:14:05,639 --> 00:14:07,972
YOU MIND IF I GO UP
AHEAD OF YOU? THANKS.

255
00:14:08,006 --> 00:14:09,439
OH, SURE.

256
00:14:09,472 --> 00:14:10,972
[ THUDDING ]

257
00:14:15,872 --> 00:14:17,506
YOU WERE RUNNING
PRETTY HARD.

258
00:14:17,539 --> 00:14:19,406
WHATEVER.
I'M NOT EVEN TIRED.

259
00:14:19,439 --> 00:14:21,972
OH, IZUMO, YOU CRACK ME UP.

260
00:14:22,006 --> 00:14:25,672
OH.
[ CELL PHONE RINGS ]

261
00:14:25,706 --> 00:14:27,906
WHOSE FREAKING PHONE'S
GOING OFF?

262
00:14:27,939 --> 00:14:29,872
HELLO? TSUBAKI HERE.
[ GROANS ]

263
00:14:29,906 --> 00:14:32,206
I'M TEACHING CLASS
RIGHT NOW, HONEY.

264
00:14:32,239 --> 00:14:34,839
WHAT? RIGHT NOW?
YOU'RE INSATIABLE.

265
00:14:34,872 --> 00:14:37,239
I'M ON MY WAY,
MY LITTLE KITTY CAT.

266
00:14:37,272 --> 00:14:40,039
OKAY, CLASS, WE'RE TAKING
A BREAK FOR A BIT.

267
00:14:40,072 --> 00:14:42,072
- [ ALL ]
HUH?
- LISTEN UP NOW.

268
00:14:42,106 --> 00:14:44,639
MOST OF THE TIME, THE REAPER
IS A PEACEFUL DEMON.

269
00:14:44,672 --> 00:14:48,139
HOWEVER, THEY CAN READ
PEOPLE'S MINDS AND ATTACK
WHEN YOU LEAST EXPECT IT.

270
00:14:48,172 --> 00:14:51,972
UNTIL I GET BACK,
YOU ARE TO STAY CLEAR
OF THE REAPER'S CHAINS.

271
00:14:52,006 --> 00:14:54,806
SCRATCH THAT.
YOU ARE NOT TO ENTER
THE ARENA.

272
00:14:54,839 --> 00:14:57,406
WE CLEAR? GOOD.
THEN I'M OUTTA HERE.

273
00:14:57,439 --> 00:14:59,839
I'M ON MY WAY,
KITTY CAT!

274
00:14:59,872 --> 00:15:03,006
YOU HEAR THAT?
TEACHER JUST CALLED SOMEONE
A KITTY CAT.

275
00:15:03,039 --> 00:15:05,172
WE'RE TAKING A BREAK
FOR A BOOTY CALL.

276
00:15:05,206 --> 00:15:07,772
ARE TEACHERS ALLOWED
TO DO THAT?
UNBELIEVABLE.

277
00:15:07,806 --> 00:15:09,906
AND HE CALLS HIMSELF
A TEACHER.

278
00:15:09,939 --> 00:15:12,272
TRUE CROSS ACADEMY
IS SUPPOSED TO BE
THIS AMAZING PLACE...

279
00:15:12,306 --> 00:15:14,906
WHERE ONLY THE HIGHLY
MOTIVATED GATHER--
WHAT B.S.

280
00:15:14,939 --> 00:15:17,106
EVEN THE STUDENTS SUCK HERE.

281
00:15:17,139 --> 00:15:19,572
SERIOUSLY, GUY,
WOULD YOU JUST
DROP IT ALREADY?

282
00:15:19,606 --> 00:15:21,172
I GOT MY REASONS
BEING HERE TOO,

283
00:15:21,206 --> 00:15:22,972
SO HOW DO YOU KNOW
I'M NOT MOTIVATED?

284
00:15:23,006 --> 00:15:25,539
I CAN TELL BY THE WAY
YOU ACT IN CLASS.

285
00:15:25,572 --> 00:15:27,839
OH, BROTHER.
HERE THEY GO AGAIN.

286
00:15:27,872 --> 00:15:29,706
[ TSUBAKI ]
THE DIRECTOR WAS THE ONE
WHO ENROLLED HIM.

287
00:15:29,739 --> 00:15:31,606
PEOPLE SAY
HE'S GOT SPECIAL ISSUES.

288
00:15:31,639 --> 00:15:36,639
[ SUGURO ]
YOU'RE JUST A SPOILED RICH KID
GETTING A FREE RIDE.

289
00:15:36,672 --> 00:15:38,672
COME ON, BON,
YOU'RE BEING IMMATURE.

290
00:15:38,706 --> 00:15:40,306
PLEASE, JUST LEAVE HIM ALONE.

291
00:15:40,339 --> 00:15:43,639
SHUT UP, BOTH OF YOU.
I KNOW WHAT I'M DOING.

292
00:15:43,672 --> 00:15:45,772
YOU SAY YOU'RE MOTIVATED?
OKAY, FINE.

293
00:15:45,806 --> 00:15:47,372
HERE'S YOUR CHANCE
TO PROVE IT.

294
00:15:47,406 --> 00:15:49,406
OH, YEAH?
HOW AM I GONNA PROVE IT?

295
00:15:49,439 --> 00:15:54,172
WITH THAT. IF YOU CAN TOUCH IT
AND GET BACK HERE
WITHOUT GETTING ATTACKED,

296
00:15:54,206 --> 00:15:55,539
YOU WIN.
HUH?

297
00:15:55,572 --> 00:15:57,439
WHEN A REAPER LOOKS
INTO YOUR EYES,

298
00:15:57,472 --> 00:15:59,272
IT'S GONNA TRY TO READ
WHATEVER YOU'RE THINKING.

299
00:15:59,306 --> 00:16:02,139
FEAR AND ANGER,
SADNESS AND JEALOUSY.

300
00:16:02,172 --> 00:16:05,672
WHATEVER IT FINDS, IT USES,
AND IF YOU LOOK AWAY,
YOU'RE DEAD...

301
00:16:05,706 --> 00:16:07,806
BECAUSE IT'LL PICK THAT MOMENT
TO ATTACK.

302
00:16:07,839 --> 00:16:11,139
THE DEAL IS IF YOU'RE SERIOUS
ABOUT BECOMING AN EXORCIST,

303
00:16:11,172 --> 00:16:13,706
YOU WON'T LOSE YOUR COOL
OVER A LITTLE OLD REAPER.

304
00:16:13,739 --> 00:16:17,006
IF YOU MAKE IT BACK HERE
IN ONE PIECE, IT'LL PROVE
YOU'RE NOT MESSING AROUND,

305
00:16:17,039 --> 00:16:18,972
AND I'LL LEAVE YOU ALONE.
WAIT, BON--

306
00:16:19,006 --> 00:16:22,872
AND I'LL GIVE IT A SHOT TOO.
THERE'S NO WAY I COULD LOSE.

307
00:16:22,906 --> 00:16:24,972
WELL?
YOU GONNA DO IT OR WHAT?

308
00:16:26,672 --> 00:16:29,506
HMM. SOUNDS LIKE FUN.
SURE. I'LL DO IT.

309
00:16:29,539 --> 00:16:33,572
- [ CHUCKLES ]
- YEAH, RIGHT.
LIKE HELL I WILL, YOU DUMBASS.

310
00:16:33,606 --> 00:16:35,872
[ GASPS ]
YOU THINK I'M CRAZY?

311
00:16:35,906 --> 00:16:38,472
WHAT IF SOMETHING HAPPENS
AND I GET KILLED?

312
00:16:38,506 --> 00:16:41,406
YEAH, 'CAUSE I CAN'T USE
MY SWORD
IN FRONT OF THESE GUYS.

313
00:16:41,439 --> 00:16:45,272
BESIDES, IF WE'RE TALKING
AMBITION, I GOT THE SAME AS YOU.

314
00:16:45,306 --> 00:16:48,739
I'M NOT GONNA RISK MY LIFE
JUST SO I CAN PROVE IT
TO YOU THOUGH.

315
00:16:48,772 --> 00:16:50,706
WHAT THE--
[ GASPS ]

316
00:16:50,739 --> 00:16:52,506
DID YOU GUYS TELL HIM?

317
00:16:52,539 --> 00:16:53,506
WELL--
WELL--

318
00:16:53,539 --> 00:16:55,172
AMBITION, MY ASS.

319
00:16:55,206 --> 00:16:57,306
YOU'RE USING THAT AS AN EXCUSE
TO CHICKEN OUT.

320
00:16:57,339 --> 00:17:00,306
- SAY WHATEVER YOU WANT, GUY.
- <i>DAMN YOU.</i>

321
00:17:00,339 --> 00:17:04,072
DAMN ALL OF YOU,
MAKING ME LOOK LIKE AN IDIOT.

322
00:17:04,106 --> 00:17:06,272
DAMN YOU ALL!

323
00:17:07,772 --> 00:17:09,639
IT'S THE BOY
FROM THE CURSED TEMPLE.

324
00:17:09,672 --> 00:17:11,872
DON'T GO NEAR HIM
OR YOU'LL GET CURSED TOO.

325
00:17:13,872 --> 00:17:15,806
[ WOMAN ]
I'M SORRY, WE CAN'T.

326
00:17:15,839 --> 00:17:17,872
MAYBE IF YOU ASKED
ONE OF THE NEIGHBORS.

327
00:17:17,906 --> 00:17:21,372
[ MAN ]
NO APOLOGIES NECESSARY, MA'AM.
SORRY TO TROUBLE YOU.

328
00:17:23,706 --> 00:17:25,739
DAD!
HUH?

329
00:17:25,772 --> 00:17:27,372
[ MAN ]
WHO WAS THAT?

330
00:17:27,406 --> 00:17:30,439
[ WOMAN ] IT WAS THAT MONK
FROM THE CURSED TEMPLE
COLLECTING OFFERINGS.

331
00:17:30,472 --> 00:17:32,406
I WAS SCARED
TO OPEN THE DOOR.

332
00:17:32,439 --> 00:17:35,506
[ MAN ]
IF ONLY THAT DAMN TEMPLE
WOULD JUST COLLAPSE ALREADY.

333
00:17:35,539 --> 00:17:37,006
[ GRUNTS ]

334
00:17:38,606 --> 00:17:39,939
[ LAUGHS ]

335
00:17:39,972 --> 00:17:42,172
THAT'S A BIT HARSH,
WOULDN'T YOU SAY?

336
00:17:43,406 --> 00:17:45,406
WHY?

337
00:17:45,439 --> 00:17:47,106
WHY IS HE LAUGHING?

338
00:17:47,139 --> 00:17:51,139
RYUGI, YOU DON'T HAVE
TO TAKE OVER THE TEMPLE
FROM ME.

339
00:17:51,172 --> 00:17:53,406
LIVE YOUR LIFE
THE WAY YOU WANT.

340
00:17:59,439 --> 00:18:01,139
HOW CAN YOU
JUST TURN YOUR BACK?

341
00:18:01,172 --> 00:18:03,906
OUR TEMPLE IS RUINED
BECAUSE OF WHAT SATAN DID.

342
00:18:06,006 --> 00:18:08,106
I HATE THIS!

343
00:18:08,139 --> 00:18:12,106
- RYUGI--
- I'M GONNA STUDY HARD
AND BECOME A GREAT EXORCIST.

344
00:18:12,139 --> 00:18:16,139
I'LL DEFEAT SATAN, THEN <i>I'M</i>
GONNA REBUILD THE TEMPLE.

345
00:18:18,472 --> 00:18:21,206
[ LAUGHS ]

346
00:18:21,239 --> 00:18:25,206
DEFEAT SATAN, HUH?
SOMETIMES YOU SAY
THE FUNNIEST THINGS.

347
00:18:25,239 --> 00:18:26,639
I'M NOT JOKING!

348
00:18:26,672 --> 00:18:28,739
I MEAN IT!

349
00:18:31,006 --> 00:18:37,172
WHY DON'T YOU DO SOMETHING?
WHY DOESN'T ANYONE FIGHT BACK?
DOESN'T THIS PISS YOU OFF?

350
00:18:37,206 --> 00:18:40,372
I'M GONNA DO IT.
STAND THERE AND WATCH ME.

351
00:18:40,406 --> 00:18:42,106
HEY, WAIT.
DON'T GO DOWN THERE.

352
00:18:42,139 --> 00:18:44,839
- [ SHIMA AND MIWA ]
BON!
- IS HE REALLY GONNA DO IT?

353
00:18:44,872 --> 00:18:47,739
OH, HE'S NOT GONNA DO
ANYTHING.
THIS IS SO LAME.

354
00:18:49,206 --> 00:18:51,272
NO WAY.

355
00:18:51,306 --> 00:18:52,972
NOT ME.

356
00:18:53,006 --> 00:18:55,406
I'M NOT A COWARD
LIKE YOU.

357
00:18:56,772 --> 00:18:59,339
I'M GONNA BE
A REAL EXORCIST
SOMEDAY.

358
00:18:59,372 --> 00:19:02,506
AND I'LL DEFEAT SATAN!

359
00:19:02,539 --> 00:19:05,106
[ LAUGHS ]

360
00:19:05,139 --> 00:19:09,739
DID YOU HEAR WHAT HE SAID?
HE'S GONNA DEFEAT SATAN.
SERIOUSLY?

361
00:19:09,772 --> 00:19:12,172
[ KAMIKI LAUGHS ]
[ HUFFS ]

362
00:19:15,472 --> 00:19:17,306
[ LAUGHING ]

363
00:19:20,106 --> 00:19:23,406
I WON'T LET YOU LAUGH AT ME...
ANYMORE!

364
00:19:23,439 --> 00:19:25,206
[ ROARING ]

365
00:19:25,239 --> 00:19:27,306
<i>- AH, CRAP!</i>
- BON!

366
00:19:32,939 --> 00:19:35,572
- HEY!
- [ RIN ]
LET GO.

367
00:19:35,606 --> 00:19:39,906
I SAID LET GO!

368
00:19:48,206 --> 00:19:50,206
[ SUGURO ]
WHAT DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE DOING?

369
00:19:50,239 --> 00:19:52,706
ARE YOU INSANE?
HUH?

370
00:19:52,739 --> 00:19:55,106
LISTEN UP.
HERE'S THE DEAL.

371
00:19:55,139 --> 00:19:59,106
I'M THE ONE WHO'S GONNA DEFEAT
SATAN, SO STAY OUT OF MY WAY!

372
00:19:59,139 --> 00:20:00,506
HUH?

373
00:20:00,539 --> 00:20:02,506
WHAT THE HELL?

374
00:20:02,539 --> 00:20:04,606
YOU'RE INSANE!

375
00:20:04,639 --> 00:20:06,339
MAN, YOU COULD'VE
GOTTEN KILLED.

376
00:20:06,372 --> 00:20:08,139
AND DON'T COPY
MY AMBITION!

377
00:20:08,172 --> 00:20:10,772
HUH? I DIDN'T COPY YOU.
IT WAS MINE FIRST.

378
00:20:10,806 --> 00:20:14,172
[ SUGURO ] NO, IT WASN'T.
I DECIDED I WAS GONNA DO IT
BEFORE YOU DID.

379
00:20:14,206 --> 00:20:16,872
[ RIN ]
WHEN? WHAT YEAR, WHAT MONTH?
WHAT DAY, HOUR, MINUTE, SECOND?

380
00:20:16,906 --> 00:20:18,639
HOW MANY TIMES
DID THE PLANETS SPIN THAT DAY?

381
00:20:18,672 --> 00:20:21,306
WHAT ARE YOU, A KID?
LOOK WHO'S TALKING.

382
00:20:21,339 --> 00:20:23,339
[ BOTH GROWLING ]

383
00:20:23,372 --> 00:20:25,739
[ YUKIO ]
YES. EVERYTHING'S
UNDER CONTROL NOW.

384
00:20:25,772 --> 00:20:28,172
EVERYONE'S SAFE.

385
00:20:28,206 --> 00:20:31,339
NO. HE DID NOT DRAW
THE KURIKARA SWORD.

386
00:20:31,372 --> 00:20:32,739
TALK TO YOU LATER.

387
00:20:32,772 --> 00:20:34,872
[ BEEPS ]

388
00:20:34,906 --> 00:20:38,339
[ SIGHS ]
ONCE UNLEASHED,
THE POWER OF SATAN...

389
00:20:38,372 --> 00:20:43,339
MIGHT PROVE TO BE
MORE UNSTOPPABLE THAN YOU EVER
IMAGINED IT COULD BE,

390
00:20:43,372 --> 00:20:45,906
SIR MEPHISTO PHELES.

391
00:20:51,372 --> 00:20:53,239
SORRY TO KEEP YOU
WAITING.

392
00:20:53,272 --> 00:20:56,072
LONG TIME NO SEE,
AMAIMON, KING OF EARTH.

393
00:20:56,106 --> 00:20:59,906
YES, IT HAS BEEN A WHILE,
HASN'T IT, BIG BROTHER?

394
00:20:59,939 --> 00:21:02,639
SO WHAT'S NEW
IN GEHENNA?

395
00:21:02,672 --> 00:21:04,972
EVERYONE
IS UNDERSTANDABLY UPSET.

396
00:21:05,006 --> 00:21:08,306
I GUESS NO ONE TOLD THEM
SATAN'S SON WAS IN ASSIAH.

397
00:21:08,339 --> 00:21:12,706
HMM. THEN PLEASE RELAY
THIS MESSAGE
TO OUR UPSET BRETHREN--

398
00:21:12,739 --> 00:21:15,439
I'VE TAKEN
OUR YOUNGEST BROTHER
UNDER MY WING.

399
00:21:15,472 --> 00:21:18,839
HE IS MATURING NICELY,
AND ALL IS GOING
RATHER WELL.

400
00:21:18,872 --> 00:21:20,706
CONSIDER IT DONE.

401
00:21:21,972 --> 00:21:24,539
WHAT'S THE MATTER?
SOMETHING ELSE ON YOUR MIND?

402
00:21:24,572 --> 00:21:28,339
OH, NO. I WAS JUST WONDERING
WHEN YOU'LL BE RETURNING
TO GEHENNA.

403
00:21:28,372 --> 00:21:32,172
YOU BETTER GO.
WOULDN'T WANT TO KEEP
OUR IMPATIENT BROTHERS WAITING.

404
00:21:32,206 --> 00:21:33,606
OKAY.

405
00:21:33,639 --> 00:21:35,339
[ WHOOSHING ]

406
00:21:35,372 --> 00:21:37,939
HMM. I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

407
00:21:37,972 --> 00:21:41,039
THIS IS PARADISE
FOR A LIBERTINE LIKE MYSELF.

408
00:21:41,072 --> 00:21:44,139
I COULD NEVER FIND
A MORE DELIGHTFUL PLAYGROUND
THAN THIS.

409
00:21:44,172 --> 00:21:48,139
BESIDES, THE FUN
IS JUST BEGINNING.

410
00:21:52,172 --> 00:21:55,172
♪ [ MAN SINGING IN JAPANESE ]

411
00:23:20,406 --> 00:23:22,472
HEY, RIN, WHAT ARE YOU UP TO?

412
00:23:22,506 --> 00:23:24,239
STUDYING, YUKIO.
WHAT ELSE?

413
00:23:24,272 --> 00:23:26,239
[ GASPS ]
IT'S THE SIGN
OF THE APOCALYPSE!

414
00:23:26,272 --> 00:23:28,006
WHAT'S THAT SUPPOSED
TO MEAN, FOUR EYES?

415
00:23:29,206 --> 00:23:30,239
[ GROWLS ]

416
00:23:30,272 --> 00:23:32,939
AH, THIS DAMN HAIR
KEEPS GETTING IN MY EYES.

417
00:23:36,239 --> 00:23:39,172
LOOK WHO IT IS.
WHAT, YOU GOT SOME JABS
FOR ME TOO?

418
00:23:39,206 --> 00:23:42,506
DIDN'T GET A CHANCE
TO TELL YOU YESTERDAY--

419
00:23:42,539 --> 00:23:45,139
- ANYWAY, THANKS.
- HUH?

420
00:23:45,172 --> 00:23:48,372
I USE THIS
TO KEEP MY HAIR UP
WHEN I STUDY AT NIGHT.

421
00:23:48,406 --> 00:23:50,772
YOU CAN BORROW IT.

422
00:23:50,806 --> 00:23:52,506
[ STAMMERS ]

423
00:23:52,539 --> 00:23:55,639
THIS IS CREEPY.
LIKE BAD LUCK CREEPY.

424
00:23:55,672 --> 00:23:58,139
[ SHOUTS ]
WHAT'S THAT
SUPPOSED TO MEAN?

425
00:23:58,172 --> 00:24:00,739
I WAS JUST TRYING
TO BE NICE,
YOU LITTLE WEASEL.

426
00:24:03,839 --> 00:24:05,272
[ RIN ]
UKOBACH?

427
00:24:05,306 --> 00:24:09,139
[ YUKIO ]
I KNOW THAT NAME.
I THINK HE'S A STOVE SPIRIT.

428
00:24:09,172 --> 00:24:12,239
[ RIN ]
LET'S DO IT! WE'RE GONNA MAKE
THE ULTIMATE LUNCH.

429
00:24:12,272 --> 00:24:14,239
[ YUKIO ]
WHAT'S GOING ON?

